&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive tax code library (GST, SST, VAT, Sales Tax)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tax rate configuration with effective dates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Historical tax rate tracking and changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tax exemption and zero-rating management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compound and cascading tax calculations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Import/export tax configurations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
